OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out nearly #40
OL,4,Cmillion over leaks and poor performance
OL,6,F"Indefensible" actions by Dwr Cymru
OL,7,FWelsh Water will see the firm pay out
OL,8,F#40 million after misleading the
OL,9,Findustry watchdog Ofwat.
OL,11,FAn investigation revealed that the
OL,12,Fwater company had misreported its
OL,13,Frecord of tackling leaks and saving
OL,14,Fwater over a period of 5 years.
OL,16,FOfwat has now ordered Welsh Water to
OL,17,Fpay #39.4 million to compensate for
OL,18,Ffailing customers.
OL,20,F, another #9.4 million will follow and
OL,21,Fsee customers bills lowered.
