OL,6,FAn extra #15 million of costs will be
OL,7,Fabsorbed by the customers, according
OL,8,Fto Ofwat.
OL,10,FIt comes amid increasing scrutiny of
OL,11,Fthe water industry and an outcry over
OL,12,Fthe sector's dire performance on
OL,13,Fleaks, raw sewage spills and poor
OL,14,Fcustomer service.
OL,16,FDavid Black, chief executive at Ofwat,
OL,17,Fsaid: "For five years, Welsh Water
OL,18,Fmisled customers and regulators on its
OL,19,Frecord of tackling leakage and saving
OL,20,Fwater.
