OL,6,F"It is simply indefensible and that is
OL,7,Fwhy we are making Welsh Water pay this
OL,8,F#40 million to benefit its customers.
OL,10,F"Today's announcement puts the
OL,11,Findustry on notice that we have the
OL,12,Fresources and will act when companies
OL,13,Ffail to meet their obligations to
OL,14,Fcustomers."
OL,16,FThe Chief Executive of Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,17,FWater has apologised for the failures
OL,18,Fin governance and management oversight
OL,19,Fprocesses.
