OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out nearly #40
OL,4,Cmillion over leaks and poor performance
OL,6,F"We are very sorry that this happened.
OL,7,FWe proactively brought this issue to
OL,8,FOfwat's attention in April 2022 having
OL,9,Fidentified it as part of our annual
OL,10,Fperformance assurance process.
OL,12,FOfwat's key conclusions as to what
OL,13,Fwent wrong align with our own
OL,14,Finvestigations that were shared with
OL,15,FOfwat together with our proposals for
OL,16,Fcustomer redress and additional
OL,17,Finvestment to tackle leakage and per
OL,18,Fcapita consumption. Rebates have
OL,19,Falready been made to 1.4 million
OL,20,Fcustomers.
