OL,6,F"Our review identified governance and
OL,7,Fmanagement oversight failures that led
OL,8,Fto the issues identified which have
OL,9,Fnow been addressed.
OL,11,F"Achieving the planned reduction in
OL,12,Fleakage will be challenging, but we
OL,13,Fhave committed a substantial increase
OL,14,Fin expenditure in this area and
OL,15,Fstrengthened the relevant operational
OL,16,Fteams to recover performance."
